ZH: 他起劲地锻炼身体。
EN: He exercises vigorously.

ZH: 她显然对这项工作很感兴趣，干得很起劲。
EN: She is obviously interested in this job and works very enthusiastically.

ZH: 小朋友们在操场上玩得很起劲。
EN: The children are playing eagerly on the playground.

ZH: 昨晚他参加一场演讲，讲得很起劲。
EN: Last night he gave a speech with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 她每天早上都会跑步，跑得很起劲。
EN: She goes for a run every morning and runs vigorously.

ZH: 那个小伙子唱歌唱得真是很起劲啊！
EN: That young man sings very enthusiastically!

ZH: 你看到他拼命工作，决心很大地时候，他总是很起劲。
EN: He always works very vigorously when he is determined.

ZH: 这个女孩子落地钳的时候做得很起劲。
EN: The girl performed the roundoff back handspring very vigorously.

ZH: 他们在园中奔跑起来，跑得很起劲。
EN: They run vigorously in the garden.

ZH: 小狗追着小猫跑，跑得很起劲。
EN: The puppy chases the kitten eagerly.

ZH: 学生们很起劲地讨论着他们的项目。
EN: The students discuss their project with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 运动员们聚在一起进行训练，全都很起劲。
EN: The athletes gather together for training, all very enthusiastic.

ZH: 那位演员在表演中表现得很起劲。
EN: That actor performs with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 隔壁的小孩在画画时，画得很起劲。
EN: The child next door is drawing with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 流行音乐是年轻人很起劲的一种音乐类型。
EN: Pop music is a type of music that young people are very enthusiastic about.

ZH: 外公每天起早锻炼，锻炼得很起劲。
EN: Grandpa exercises vigorously every day.

ZH: 她很起劲地擦拭镜子，把它擦得一尘不染。
EN: She cleans the mirror energetically, leaving it spotless.

ZH: 这位厨师砍菜切菜煮东西，煮得很起劲。
EN: The chef chops, slices, and cooks with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 他对烹饪很感兴趣，所以煮菜的时候总是很起劲。
EN: He is interested in cooking, so he always cooks with great enthusiasm.

ZH: 大家在一起演练的时候，都很起劲。
EN: Everyone is very enthusiastic when practicing together.
